@rochasofficial dreams

Everyone loves to get mail! I’m creating a monthly print to send out to anyone who wants one. The idea is very simple: DM me if you want to receive a printed image once a month, along with your mailing address, and I will send you something in return. Each month will be a new image- anything from an analog photograph to an AI image… all I ask in return is that you take care of the prints. So much of our industry has become a discarding of this beautiful art form and I would like to do something small to keep the final stage of a photograph intact.
